Class FakeThrowablePrinter

  • java.lang.Object
    • ccre.workarounds.ThrowablePrinter
      • ccre.workarounds.FakeThrowablePrinter

  • public class FakeThrowablePrinter
extends ThrowablePrinter
    A fake throwable printer for when nothing better is available. This just prints out the result of .toString() on the Throwable object.
